02:22.740 --> 02:25.640
said by some to be the most
dangerous in the world.

02:49.050 --> 02:51.360
Located between India and Tibet,

02:51.390 --> 02:53.330
Bhutan, about the size
of Switzerland,

02:53.360 --> 02:56.330
is caught between
the old world and the new.

03:01.580 --> 03:04.680
Thimphu is Bhutan's capital
and largest city.

03:04.720 --> 03:08.450
It has a rapidly growing
population of 100,000,

03:08.480 --> 03:11.860
as Bhutanese have begun
the inevitable move away

03:11.900 --> 03:14.040
from a rural,
agrarian lifestyle.

03:19.280 --> 03:22.460
Tourism was only allowed
starting in the 1970s.

03:22.490 --> 03:25.570
The amount of foreign visitors
each year is strictly limited

03:25.600 --> 03:29.740
to protect Bhutan's culture
and environment.

03:29.780 --> 03:34.470
There are no Starbucks,
no KFCs, no King or Clown.

03:34.510 --> 03:37.790
Basically, they don't
want you to come here...

03:37.820 --> 03:40.820
at least en masse.

03:43.480 --> 03:46.070
- Watch your head.
