In Bhutan, women are the boss.

24:25.830 --> 24:27.970
Women inherit whatever
the parents own.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.310
It's not the sons.

24:29.350 --> 24:30.993
Always? All inheritance
goes to the woman?

24:31.000 --> 24:32.730
