24:32.760 --> 24:34.140
- What is this?
- Wow.

24:34.180 --> 24:37.040
This is ara,
with some Cordyceps in it.

24:37.080 --> 24:39.220
- What? That is a Cordycep?
- Right there.

24:39.250 --> 24:41.220
- That is the Cordycep.
- Which is?

24:41.250 --> 24:43.640
Essentially,
the Cordycep is a fungus

24:43.670 --> 24:47.610
which infects the larvae
of the ghost moths.

24:47.640 --> 24:50.330
A caterpillar that has been
invaded by fungus.

24:50.370 --> 24:52.990
Essentially takes over
the whole larvae,

24:53.020 --> 24:55.200
kills it, sort of mummifies
the whole thing.

24:55.230 --> 24:57.270
Then in the spring,
it protrudes out again.

24:57.300 --> 24:59.930
Is there any caterpillar
left at the end or is it fo...

24:59.960 --> 25:01.613
Sort of like fossilized?
It's just a fossil.

25:01.620 --> 25:03.690
Meaning it is not meat.

25:03.730 --> 25:04.660
It is vegetarian.

25:04.690 --> 25:06.350
Right.

25:06.380 --> 25:09.560
Cordyceps are the new
profit center for a culture

25:09.590 --> 25:12.700
that used to revolve almost
entirely around the yak.

25:12.730 --> 25:15.220
Wow, so this stuff
costs how much a kilo?

25:15.250 --> 25:18.740
Um, on average,
it's about, uh, 20,000.

25:18.770 --> 25:20.120
- 20,000 U.S.?
- Dollars.

25:20.160 --> 25:21.850
- Oh, that's a lot.
