25:32.100 --> 25:33.200
- Hepatitis?
- Yeah.

25:33.240 --> 25:34.690
- Piles, eh?
- What is piles?

25:34.720 --> 25:36.210
- Hemorrhoids.
- Oh.

25:36.240 --> 25:37.753
And the Chinese athletes
have been taking it

25:37.760 --> 25:40.380
for quite some time.
So they're doping on, uh...

25:40.420 --> 25:42.413
- They're doping on fungus.
- They're doping on fungus.

25:42.420 --> 25:43.970
Yeah.

25:44.010 --> 25:45.630
It's pretty tasty.

25:45.660 --> 25:49.670
Yeah, it also says
that you produce more semen.

25:49.700 --> 25:52.150
I don't know how far
is true, but...

25:52.190 --> 25:53.880
So what about the...
