25:53.910 --> 25:55.120
The Divine Madman.

25:55.160 --> 25:57.050
Maybe the guy was, you know,

25:57.090 --> 25:58.400
eating a lot of Cordyceps.

25:58.430 --> 26:00.610
Exactly.

